<body>
    <h1>Resonance Breathing Technique</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p>Resonance breathing is also called as coherent breathing and wor=
ks by focusing and balancing your inhales and exhales to a specific rhythm.=
 Every person has a slightly different Resonant breathing rate which is oft=
en between the rate of 5-6 breaths per minute. This technique can help bala=
nce the body systems, nudge the ANS towards a homeostatic state and reduce =
stress.</p>
<h2 id=3D"ResonanceBreathingTechnique-Instructions"><img class=3D"emoticon =
emoticon-blue-star" data-emoji-id=3D"1f4d8" data-emoji-shortname=3D":blue_b=
ook:" data-emoji-fallback=3D"\uD83D\uDCD8" src=3D"5b59babcae7cb54d196aaff48=
25f4bdf56c2bc39e071c1fbc3297ad49d2560f7" width=3D"16" height=3D"16" data-em=
oticon-name=3D"blue-star" alt=3D"(blue star)">&nbsp;Instructions</h2>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Find a comfortable sitting or lying position.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Inhale slowly and steadily through your nose for a count of 5.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Exhale slowly and completely through your nose for a count of 5.</p></li=
>
<li>
<p>Continue this pattern, maintaining a steady and even pace.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Focus on the smooth transition between inhales and exhales.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Practice breathing for 4-5 mins for optimum benefit.</p></li>
</ol>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-inf=
ormation">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-informa=
tion-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p><strong>Biofeedback:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Pay attention to the soothing rhythm of your breath.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Feel your body gradually relaxing with each breath.</p></li>
</ul>
<p>Notice a sense of balance and harmony as you synchronize your breathing.=
</p>
</div>
</div>
    </div>
</body>
